comments: Carter Jr. (ORL) reaches in and makes marginal contact with Doncic's (DAL) off-arm that does not affect his SQBR.
FInney-Smith (DAL) makes marginal contact to Carter Jr.'s (ORL) arm as he secures the rebound.
Bullock (DAL) reaches in and makes contact to Anthony's (ORL) leg during his drive that is marginal.
Finney-Smith (DAL) makes contact to Wagner's (ORL) body during the drive but the contact is marginal.
Bullock (DAL) turns along with Wagner (ORL) and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Carter Jr. (ORL) dislodges Finney-Smith (DAL) from his position during the rebound.
Kleber (DAL) reaches in and makes contact to Suggs' (ORL) arm that affects his SQBR.
Kleber (DAL) makes contact to Carter Jr.'s (ORL) arm as he defends the pass that affects his  SQBR.
